<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title> Im Vahn Harvey Banilad | My Personal Website</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background: #f4f6f9;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background: #111827;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        header p {
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        nav {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        nav a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #3b82f6;
        }

        section {
            padding: 60px 10%;
        }

        .about, .projects, .contact {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        h2 {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #111827;
        }

        .projects-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }

        .project-card {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .project-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        .contact a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-right: 15px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            background: #3b82f6;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .contact a:hover {
            background: #2563eb;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background: #111827;
            color: white;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }

        @media(max-width: 768px) {
            section {
                padding: 40px 5%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Hi! Im Vahn Harvey Banilad </h1>
    <p>Web Developer | Designer | Creator</p>
    <nav>
        <a href="#about">About</a>
        <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section id="about" class="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>
        Hello! I'm Vahn Harvey Banilad, Im 17 years old and I am a Senior High Student at Padre Pio Child
        Development School. My Hobbies include playing video games, watching movies, and learning new things about programming.
        My Dream Job is to become a Software Engineer and work for a big tech company like Google, Microsoft, or Apple. I am passionate about technology and I am always eager to learn and grow in the field of programming.
    </p>
</section>

<section id="projects" class="projects">
    <h2>My Projects</h2>
    <div class="projects-grid">
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>Project One</h3>
            <p>A short description of your project goes here.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>Project Two</h3>
            <p>A short description of your project goes here.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project-card">
            <h3>Project Three</h3>
            <p>A short description of your project goes here.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="contact" class="contact">
    
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 Vahn Harvey Banilad. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
